<section>
    <h3 class = "section-header">Project 0 - The Setup</h3>

    <p>So the first project was to actually get everything set up. I knew I wanted to add the things I learned in the bootcamp to the site, and that began with adding the items into the environment. The packages used at this part of the bootcamp were:</p>

